breadCrumbs.text: View or download your supplier list

title: Find suppliers and run your procurement online.
line5_mcf: To add or amend your selected services and see other suppliers, click 'Change' below.
line8_mcf: The suppliers below offer all the services you selected. Contact these suppliers for any pre-market engagement.
line1: View or download your shortlisted suppliers
line5: To contact other suppliers not listed below, you’ll need to delete this list.
line6: [ You can view supplier's rate cards from this page. ]
line7: [ If you'd like to look at additional details for each suppliers please visit the Search suppliers page on the main CCS website. The page will open on a new tab. ]
line8: The suppliers below offer all the services you need. Contact these suppliers for any pre-market engagement or call-off events. You can view suppliers’ rate cards from this page.
line9: Further details of each supplier can be found on the CCS webiste on the Search suppliers page. The page will open on a new tab.
line17: View rate card and contact details
